description: Demolition of existing buildings on site and erection of a part 4, part 5, part 6 storey building plus basement on Goldhawk Road and Hammersmith Grove, and detached single storey building to the rear, to comprise 63 residential units and 70sqm of commercial floorspace (Use Classes A1, A2 or B1) on the ground floor of the Goldhawk Road frontage; residents' car parking in the basement; landscaping to Hammersmith Grove frontage and communal courtyard.
